# 🟡 Part 1（每题≈30秒）

## Q1：Do you like reading books?

### 🎯 8.0 Answer

> Well, to be honest, I really enjoy reading books, especially novels and self-improvement books.
> The main reason is that reading helps me relax and at the same time learn new things.
> For example, I usually read before going to bed, which helps me unwind after a long day.
> So overall, I think reading is both enjoyable and beneficial.

### 🇨🇳 翻译

说实话，我真的很喜欢读书，尤其是小说和自我提升类书籍。
主要原因是阅读既能让我放松，也能让我学到新知识。
比如，我通常在睡前阅读，这可以让我在忙碌一天后放松下来。
总的来说，我认为阅读既有趣又有益。

---

### ✨ 可复用表达

* to be honest
* unwind after a long day
* both enjoyable and beneficial

---

## Q2：How often do you read?

### 🎯 Answer

> I would say I read quite regularly.
> I try to read almost every day, even if it's just for a short time.
> For example, I usually spend about 20 to 30 minutes reading before I go to sleep.
> So I would say reading has become part of my daily routine.

### 🇨🇳 翻译

我会说我阅读得挺频繁的。
我几乎每天都会读一点，即使时间不长。
比如，我通常会在睡前读20到30分钟。
所以我觉得阅读已经成为我日常生活的一部分。

---

## Q3：Did you like reading when you were a child?

### 🎯 Answer

> Yes, I did enjoy reading when I was a child.
> Back then, I was really into storybooks and fairy tales.
> For example, I remember spending hours reading after school.
> So I think reading has always been an important part of my life.

### 🇨🇳 翻译

是的，我小时候很喜欢读书。
那时候我特别喜欢故事书和童话。
比如，我记得放学后经常一读就是几个小时。
所以我觉得阅读一直是我生活中很重要的一部分。

