## Q1：Why do some people dislike reading?

### 🎯 Answer

> I think there are several reasons for that.
> One main reason is that reading requires a lot of concentration, which some people find difficult.
> For example, compared to watching videos, reading can feel more tiring.
> So as a result, some people prefer more relaxing forms of entertainment.

### 🇨🇳 翻译

我觉得原因有很多。
一个主要原因是阅读需要高度集中注意力，而这对一些人来说比较困难。
比如，相比看视频，阅读可能更让人疲惫。
所以有些人更喜欢更轻松的娱乐方式。

---

## Q2：Do you think people read less nowadays?

### 🎯 Answer

> Yes, I think people tend to read less nowadays.
> This is mainly because of the rise of technology and social media.
> For example, people spend more time on their phones instead of reading books.
> So overall, reading is becoming less common in daily life.

### 🇨🇳 翻译

是的，我觉得现在人们阅读得更少了。
这主要是因为科技和社交媒体的发展。
比如，人们花更多时间在手机上，而不是读书。
所以总体来说，阅读在日常生活中变得不那么常见了。

